      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "OUR ULTIMATE GRACY NZ (5) has been competitive of late and kept the ball rolling last time when 2.6 metres from the winner in third in a higher-graded race at Horsham. Draws wider but is suited dropping in class and owns a good record at this longer distance so could grab a well-deserved win. MISTER JIMARINGLE (2) had a tough draw in his latest appearance at Melton so that result can be forgiven. Had recorded a string of placings at this venue prior and is likely to get all the favours from this nice draw so is worth another chance. OWEN THE SAINTS (1) was held up last time but came from much wider than this to score at Charlton prior. Player from the ace draw. FLOJOS BEST (4) draws a couple of spots lower than when fifth at her most recent appearance at Shepparton. Include.",
